</bookmark>
<h3 id="hd_id3149213">Parallel</h3>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147740"><variable id="seitenumlauftext"><ahelp hid=".">Wraps text on all four sides of the border frame of the object.</ahelp>
</variable></paragraph>
